 all these results are obtained in the chiral limit, numerical\ncalculations with finite quark masses show that the corrections are extremely\nsmall. Some of these calculations are repeated in the Hirn-Sanz model and\nsimilar results are obtained.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 21 Oct 2009 03:33:06 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 14 Jan 2010 09:43:56 GMT"}],"update_date":"2014-11-20"}
